      <li><a href="http://library.columbia.edu/help/using-this-site.html">Libraries Website Help</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://library.columbia.edu/research/askalibrarian.html">Ask a Librarian</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://library.columbia.edu/find/clio.html">CLIO Help</a></li>
